STATE of North Carolina
v.
Anthony DOVE No. 131P01-15 Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 30, 2019 Anthony Dove, for Dove, Anthony. Sherri Lawrence, Assistant Attorney General, Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 7th of January 2019 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Lenoir County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 30th of January 2019."

Ervin, J. recused
